Folder structure:

project/
│
├── bot/
│   ├── main.py            # Telegram bot entry point
│   ├── handlers/          # Command handlers split into files
│   │   └── airdrop.py
│   │   └── start.py
│   │   └── balance.py
│   └── utils/             # Helper functions for parsing, formatting, validation
│       └── telegram_helpers.py
│
├── backend/
│   ├── app.py             # FastAPI/Flask backend entry point
│   ├── wallet.py          # Wallet generation, signing, RPC calls
│   ├── database.py        # User storage, rate limits, logs
│   └── config.py          # RPC URL, private key, token contract, settings
│
├── database/
│   └── airdrop.db         # SQLite file (or migrations folder if using SQLAlchemy)
│
├── contracts/             # Optional: ABI files or contract addresses
│   └── token_abi.json
│
└── README.md              # Setup instructions

